{"article_id":"c5nSwIBsmGTRocDh","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Former acting FBI Director Andrew McCabe testifies before a Senate Intelligence Committee hearing , June 7 , 2017 .","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"( Aaron P. Bernstein/Reuters )","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"It ' s too early to take away any clear lessons from the Trump era , except one :","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"Whatever you do ,","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"never fire the FBI director .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"Yes , as president , it is fully within your power to cashier inferior executive-branch officers .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"But","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"if the aftermath of the James Comey firing is any indication ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"it risks backlash from FBI and Justice Department officials","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"who will take umbrage","depth":12},{"id":10,"text":"- and extraordinary steps in response .","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"This is the upshot of the 60 Minutes interview of former Deputy Director Andrew McCabe .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"The Comey firing was ham-fisted and unsettling","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"given the ongoing investigation of Russian interference into the 2016 election .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"But what ensued was an embarrassing freakout by law-enforcement officials","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"entrusted with awesome powers .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"According to McCabe ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein brought up","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"invoking the 25th Amendment .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"It ' s worth considering how this Rube Goldberg amendment is supposed to work :","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"The vice president takes power","depth":12},{"id":21,"text":"if he and a majority of the Cabinet declare in writing to the Senate and the House","depth":13},{"id":22,"text":"that the president is \" unable to discharge the powers and duties of his office . \"","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"Then the president can contest the declaration , also in writing , to the Senate and the House .","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"If the vice president and a majority of the Cabinet still say","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"he can ' t serve ,","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"Congress has 21 days to vote on the question .","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"If two-thirds of both houses says","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"he can ' t ,","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"the vice president remains acting president .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"Anyone","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"who believes","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"that this was a remotely plausible or appropriate means","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"to depose Donald Trump","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"should have his own ability","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"to discharge his duties","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"examined .","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"First of all , Trump obviously was perfectly capable","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"of discharging his duties ;","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"he just discharged them in a way","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"alarming to McCabe and Rosenstein .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"His response to an effort by his Cabinet","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"to join such an exercise","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"would have been to fire anyone involved ,","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"which he could have done","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"because , again , he wasn ' t incapacitated .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"McCabe also says","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"that Rosenstein twice discussed wearing a wire","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"to record the president","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"and wasn ' t joking .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"( A source told the New York Times","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"when it originally broke the story","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"that Rosenstein meant it sarcastically ;","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"his own denials have been carefully worded . )","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"The FBI didn ' t go this far ,","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"but it did open ,","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"per McCabe ,","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"two probes into the president","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"to determine","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"if he was a Russian agent","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"or had obstructed justice .","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"Consider the lunacy of this :","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"By providing Trump with a memo","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"justifying Comey ' s firing ,","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"Rosenstein participated in the scheme","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"that the FBI considered a possible crime , or the culmination of a Russian plot .","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"Then Rosenstein turned around","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"and appointed a special counsel ,","depth":16},{"id":68,"text":"whom he oversaw ,","depth":16},{"id":69,"text":"to investigate the possible crime","depth":16},{"id":70,"text":"to which he was a party .","depth":16},{"id":71,"text":"It ' s also absurd that the FBI officials considered the firing of Comey to be potential obstruction of the investigation","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"that they were continuing ,","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"and indeed making more serious","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"by making the president an explicit target .","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"The comments","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"that Trump made about Russia","depth":14},{"id":77,"text":"that McCabe and Co. found so disturbing","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"were hardly damning .","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"In his cover letter over Rosenstein ' s memo , Trump mentioned","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"that Comey had told him three times","depth":15},{"id":81,"text":"that he wasn ' t under investigation .","depth":15},{"id":82,"text":"This was true ,","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"and Trump was frustrated","depth":15},{"id":84,"text":"that Comey wouldn ' t make it public .","depth":15},{"id":85,"text":"That doesn ' t make him a Russian agent .","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"In his notorious Lester Holt interview , Trump said","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"he fired Comey","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"because there wasn ' t anything to him and Russia .","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"He didn ' t say","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"he wanted to shut down the probe ;","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"indeed , he said","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"he understood","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"it would now probably go on longer .","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"Perhaps Trump ' s comments in his ill-considered meeting with the Russian foreign minister and ambassador in the immediate aftermath of the Comey firing were worse ,","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"but it ' s hard to say","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"absent a transcript .","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"What McCabe ' s version strongly suggests is that the FBI took upon itself to be a check on the president of the United States .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"This is not its appointed role in our system .","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"If the president abuses his powers ,","depth":13},{"id":100,"text":"that ' s a matter for Congress","depth":15},{"id":101,"text":"to take up ,","depth":15},{"id":102,"text":"not for executive-branch officials","depth":15},{"id":103,"text":"whose panic eclipsed their judgment .","depth":15},{"id":104,"text":"Something to Consider","depth":4},{"id":105,"text":"If you enjoyed this article ,","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"we have a proposition for you :","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"Join NRPLUS .","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"Members get all of our content","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"( including the magazine ) ,","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"no paywalls or content meters , an advertising-minimal experience , and unique access to our writers and editors","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"( conference calls , social-media groups , etc. ) .","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"And importantly , NRPLUS members help keep NR going .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"Consider it ?","depth":5},{"id":114,"text":"If you enjoyed this article ,","depth":4},{"id":115,"text":"and were stimulated by its contents ,","depth":4},{"id":116,"text":"we have a proposition for you :","depth":4},{"id":117,"text":"Join NRPLUS .","depth":4},{"id":118,"text":"LEARN MORE","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":237,"left":232,"right":236,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":232,"left":120,"right":231,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":120,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":231,"left":221,"right":230,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":221,"left":147,"right":220,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":129,"right":146,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":122,"right":128,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":2,"right":121,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":121,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":128,"left":127,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":5,"right":126,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":126,"left":6,"right":125,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":125,"left":7,"right":124,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":124,"left":8,"right":123,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":132,"right":145,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":130,"right":131,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":130,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":131,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":134,"right":144,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":134,"left":16,"right":133,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent